<h3 id="step-6-offer-to-install">Step 6: Offer to Install</h3>

<p>If the user wants to proceed, you can install the skill for them:</p>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><table class="rouge-table"><tbody><tr><td class="rouge-gutter gl"><pre class="lineno">1
</pre></td><td class="rouge-code"><pre>npx skills add &lt;owner/repo@skill&gt; <span class="nt">-g</span> <span class="nt">-y</span>
</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></code></pre></div></div>

<p>The <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">-g</code> flag installs globally (user-level) and <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">-y</code> skips confirmation prompts.</p>

